T02TD2161E:256a-1: n'i l'am ba ra dha ra badzra p'a ni ho ma bi dhi n'a ma /
T02TD2161E:256a-3: phyag na rdo rje gos sngon po can gyi sbyin sreg gi cho ga zhes bya ba /
T02TD2161E:256a-4: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2161E:256a-5: gang zhig med par de mi 'byung //
T02TD2161E:256a-6: des na de la 'jug pa brtsam //
T02TD2161E:256a-7: de la 'dir thab khung gru gsum pa mgo lhor bstan pa'i nang du /
T02TD2161E:256a-8: khro bo'i rdo rje sor brgyad pa bkod de /
T02TD2161E:256a-9: thal ba dang sol bas nag por byugs la dri chu dang bong bu dang rnga mo'i rtug pas byug par bya'o //
T02TD2161E:256a-16: me tog nag po ni mchod yon no //
T02TD2161E:256a-20: bdud rtsi lnga sbyar ba'i spos so //
T02TD2161E:256a-22: dri chu dang til nag po sbyar ba ni dri chab /
T02TD2161E:256a-23: dri chen dang mi sha bsres pa'i lha bshos te /
T02TD2161E:256a-24: de rnams g-yas su gzhag par bya'o //
T02TD2161E:256b-1: bdud rtsi lnga dang bsres pa'i yungs mar rnams ni dgang gzar du blugs te khrag tu byas la dbul lo //
T02TD2161E:256b-2: shing tsher ma can gyi yam shing dang /
T02TD2161E:256b-15: bya rog gi sha rnams dang /
T02TD2161E:256b-17: rnga mo'i rtug pa rnams ni sreg rdzas te /
T02TD2161E:256b-18: sha dang rus par bsam mo //
T02TD2161E:256b-20: rang lha'i rnal 'byor byas la rdzas byin gyis brlabs nas bgegs bskrad do //
T02TD2161E:256b-22: sme sha can nam rdo las byung ba'am /
T02TD2161E:256b-25: aom badzra p'a ni ma h'a kro dha dzv'a la dzva'a la h'um h'um h'um phat phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD2161E:256b-27: me 'bar ba'i nang du ram las thab khung bskyed la de'i nang du h'um las nyi ma'i steng du aom a'a h'um las 'khor lo dang /
T02TD2161E:256b-30: de nas khro bo'i me lha shin tu khros pa /
T02TD2161E:256b-31: skra kham pa gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD2161E:256b-32: 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro ba /
T02TD2161E:256b-34: g-yas na rdo rje dang skyabs sbyin /
T02TD2161E:256b-35: g-yon na dril bu dang dbyug pa /
T02TD2161E:256b-36: ram las me dang rlung gi dkyil 'khor la bsams te /
T02TD2161E:256b-37: ye shes sems dpa' dgug pa dang /
T02TD2161E:256b-40: dbang du byas nas der byin rlabs dang /
T02TD2161E:256b-42: khrus gsol nas zhal gdangs pa'i nang du mchod rdzas dang sreg rdzas rnams 'dis dbul te /
T02TD2161E:256b-43: aom badzra p'a ni ma h'u bh'u ta dzv'a la ya sarba bhasmim ku ru sarba dusht'am ma ma che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat ces pas gsad par bya'o //
T02TD2161E:256b-44: de nas me 'bar bas rgyur gyur pa'am /
T02TD2161E:256b-45: yang na de'i snying gar dpal phyag na rdo rje gos sngon po can sgrub thabs las ji skad gsungs pa bzhin nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas par bskyed nas ye shes sems dpa' snga ma bzhin bstims la /
T02TD2161E:256b-46: de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang bskur bar bya'o //
T02TD2161E:256b-47: de nas phreng ba'i sngags la m'a ra ya dang bcas pas mchod rdzas snga ma bzhin du dbul lo //
T02TD2161E:257a-3: rdzas lhag ma rnams me lha la phul nas /
T02TD2161E:257a-4: aom bdag dang gzhan gyi don rnams ni //
T02TD2161E:257a-5: bsgrubs te sbyin sreg bzhes nas kyang //
T02TD2161E:257a-6: slar yang 'byon par mdzad nas kyang //
T02TD2161E:257a-7: bdag la sngags kyi dngos grub stsol //
T02TD2161E:257a-8: zhes me lha gshegs su gsol lo //
T02TD2161E:257a-9: de'i rjes su dam tshig pa rang la bsdus te /
T02TD2161E:257a-11: nyung bar 'dod na bla ma'i zhal nas ji skad gsungs pa bzhin du 'di la 'jug par bya'o //
T02TD2161E:257a-12: phyag na rdo rje'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga mdor bsdus pa zhes bya ba nam gru'i rigs las byung ba dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon dz'a ba ri pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2161E:257a-14: // / ba la po'i pandi ta de ba p'u rna ma ti dang /
T02TD2161E:257a-15: lo ts'a ba dge slong chos kyi bzang pos bsgyur ba'o//
